Shop,Pro,is,a,hosted,store,and,shopping,cart,The,service,allows,online,businesses,to,market,and,sell,their,products,and,services,by,accepting,online,payments,With,the,Shop,Pro,API,developers,can,build,new,applications,to,interact,with,the,platform,Update,listings,orders,customers,and,products,using,the,SOAP,protocol,with,responses,formatted,in,XML